com.opengamma.strata.basics.market

Interface MarketData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImmutableMarketData, SingleCalculationMarketData

    public interface MarketData
    Provides access to market data, such as curves, surfaces and time-series.

    Market data is looked up using subclasses of MarketDataKey. All data is valid for a single date, defined by getValuationDate(). When performing calculations with scenarios, only the data of a single scenario is accessible.

    The standard implementation is ImmutableMarketData.
